    "Pharmacology": {
      "text": "Half-life:\n1.6 ± 0.38 hours (single dose), 2.66 ± 0.4 hours (multiple doses)\nMetabolism:\nExcretion:\nUrine 88%, Feces 6%\nMechanism of Action:\nInhibits bacterial cell wall synthesis by binding to penicillin-binding proteins",
